# rules for creating a variable name
In [6]:
# 1)name should start with wit alphabet and underscore only(_)
# ex. abc=10, _ab_=10 , full_name='AK SK'
# 2)It should not start with number
# EX. 
# a12b=100
# 12ab=90
# 3)white spaces are not allowed in variable name 
# full123name='sdfghj sdfghj'
# 4)special characters are not allowed 
# #,@
# 5)keyword are not allowed 
# shortcut key for comments= ctrl+/
# shortcut key for execution = shift+Enter
